name: .FO File Extension
summary: Learn about .FO files and view a list of programs that open them.

description: Formatting Objects Form that saves data in a standard XML format; XSL-FO (also called XSL) is a markup language that defines how XML data is formatted for the screen, print, or other type of media.

content: Because XSL-FO forms use standard XML formatting, data entered into XSL-FO forms can be integrated with any database that supports XML. Data can be collected online or offline and forms may include security features and form validation.
XSL-FO stands for "Extensible Stylesheet Language - Formatting Objects."
